ial Fundamentals provides resources designed to help you budget your money wisely in order to live within your means. Discover also offers free alerts for cardholders that notify you when you’re nearing your credit limit or a bill-payment due date.","Another top benefit with the Miles by Discover® Card is the company&#39;s fraud-prevention capabilities. Through constant monitoring of your account, Discover&#39;s unique technology knows to notify you if there are unusual transactions or other signs of fraudulent activity on your account, including telephone calls to alert you if the situation is serious. Discover will also provide emergency card replacement for members whose credit cards are lost or stolen."]},"id":"bac1268e-89bd-4723-aad8-8fa16f0bcd47","type":"text"},{"data":{"text":"Rewards Benefits"},"id":"b3728fb7-4d8c-4551-9351-d6b284ffbc89","type":"heading"},{"data":{"paragraphs":["There is a set of Must-Have features that go along with travel credit cards, and the Miles by Discover® Card has the full slate. With this card, you earn one point for each dollar you spend on the account. Then, you get double miles for the first $3,000 in travel and restaurant purchases you make every year. On top of that, you can earn 10,000 Bonus Miles with every $2,000 in purchases within the first 6 months – up to 20,000 Bonus Miles. Like other reward credit card programs, you can also get bonus points by making purchases at an exclusive online shopping mall.","Another excellent feature that comes with the Miles by Discover® Card is its financial education program. This suite of information offers several separate categories designed to teach cardholders how to best utilize their credit cards in a safe and responsible way. Some of the tools offered include a Savings Solutions center, a Credit Management tool, an identity-theft prevention guide, and articles and videos regarding personal financial responsibility.","Another Discover benefit is that, as a cardholder, you are not liable for fraudulent charges made with your account cards in case your wallet is stolen or your PC is hacked. You can have peace of mind knowing you won’t be paying for things that thieves ultimately receive when you work with Discover.","Free online account access and mobile device accessibility are other benefits you can expect with Mile by Discover. All you have to do is log in to your account from any computer with an internet connection and you can manage your money safely and securely."]},"id":"ac62846d-744e-4fee-9652-6affb5d3341e","type":"text"},{"data":{"text":"APR*"},"id":"f79baeca-ab7c-4bc5-a049-3f98596bd93c","type":"heading"},{"data":{"paragraphs":["The Miles by Discover® Card offers its cardholders a great deal on interest rates. You’ll pay no Annual Percentage Rate (APR) on purchases and no APR for all balance transfers for 12 months. This feature, paired with advice from Discover on money management, can help you get on the path to debt freedom quickly. This is rare among rewards card programs.","After the introductory periods, your rates will go up to 10.99 to 19.99%, depending on your credit qualifications. You’ll also get a grace period of 25 days. Another benefit – one that is not historically common in rewards programs – is no annual fees. If you repay your purchases within the grace period, that means you can profit from the Miles by Discover® Card benefits at nearly no cost to you.","If you miss a payment or pay late, your rate will jump to between 15.99% and 20.99% indefinitely. This rate, while punishing, is nearly 10 percentage points less than most competitors&#39; penalty interest rates. The APR for cash advances with the Miles by Discover® Card is 24.99%. We recommend using cash advances only as a last resort."]},"id":"0872a2d0-5d92-44e6-919e-5112f7a16eec","type":"text"},{"data":{"text":"Fees &amp; Penalties"},"id":"a10b6ed1-0a63-4c79-b86e-f6e08465990f","type":"heading"},{"data":{"paragraphs":["No one wants to be charged fees, but sometimes situations occur that make these extra costs inevitable. the Miles by Discover® Card cardholders can expect a late fee of up to $35, depending upon the total balance overdue. There is no over-credit-limit fee, which we appreciate.","Other fees accrue in the normal course of business, especially for regular travelers. There is a fee of either 5% or $10 for each cash-advance transaction and a 2-percent fee for charges made outside of the U.S. This rate recently dropped by 1%; it now falls below the industry standard for overseas transactions."]},"id":"608e58b1-0355-4ab8-9c25-2d744002d7ce","type":"text"},{"data":{"text":"Key Features"},"id":"2c4b171c-d16f-4eaa-b533-702af5f0b0e0","type":"heading"},{"data":{"paragraphs":["Many credit card rewards programs go beyond the call of duty by providing extra protections for their customers, and the Miles by Discover® Card is no exception. The company offers benefits such as auto rental and travel-accident insurance, in addition to superior anti-fraud protection, mentioned above. In fact, the Miles by Discover® Card offers a 24-hour fraud specialist who can help you one on one at any time."]},"id":"c0bb6e99-7e31-4c58-87a1-d754b3d1d1d2","type":"text"},{"data":{"text":"Member Support"},"id":"84dcf68d-39d3-4682-80bb-1b45ce428adb","type":"heading"},{"data":{"paragraphs":["the Miles by Discover® Card puts a focus on customer service and customer protection. If you call with a complaint, the Miles by Discover® Card offers a guarantee that you will be able to speak to a real person within 60 seconds. Your representative will then be able to assist you or direct you to an individual who can.","Discover offers 24-hour customer support, both through email and by phone. This is a great feature because your card won’t always stop working during business hours. We were also very impressed with Discover&#39;s FAQs section. All of our questions that weren&#39;t answered there were answered quickly via email correspondence."]},"id":"60672d6b-b925-4a4f-8313-e5b6dfdbf7ca","type":"text"},{"data":{"text":"Summary"},"id":"e210a43b-10b1-40ae-a79f-df013313db15","type":"heading"},{"data":{"paragraphs":["The Miles by Discover® Card is an excellent rewards credit card choice for high rollers and penny pinchers alike. Its low APRs and low fees, in addition to a plethora of features, make it stand out from the fray. We especially like how adamant Discover is about supporting its customers. We recommend this card particularly for people who can use help keeping their finances in order."]},"id":"965f654e-a9ba-40c2-b557-09941db67f9c","type":"text"}]],"body":null,"legacyId":"product_review_page_3426","url":"/miles-by-discover-review","authors":[{"email":"","slug":"top-ten-reviews-staff","url":"/author/top-ten-reviews-staff","dateCreated":"2019-04-17T20:46:58Z","name":"Top Ten Reviews Staff","dateModified":"2019-04-17T20:46:58Z","id":"EcXXb3s8QKwvex3rQshgX5","dateImported":null,"site":"toptenreviews"}],"territories":["US","GB"],"companies":[],"dateCreated":"2009-07-23T19:09:54Z","datePublished":"2009-07-23T19:09:54Z","name":"Miles by Discover® Card","synopsis":"Editor’s Note: This product has been removed from our side-by-side comparison because it has been replaced by another product].","review":{"rating":88,"verdict":"The Miles by Discover&#174; Card offers an incredible value with low basic interest rates and a wide range of features geared toward rewarding travelers and protecting borrowers.","pros":["This credit card offers the lowest maximum APR of all the cards we reviewed, gratifying dining rewards and thousands of free flight miles in the first year."],"cons":["Your penalty interest rates are low with the Miles by Discover&#174; Card, but late-payment fees and over-the-limit fees are expensive."]},"strapline":"Editor’s Note: This product has been removed from our side-by-side comparison because it has been replaced by another product].","language":"en","dateModified":"2009-07-28T21:55:58Z","id":"7mw5QApmMVo8gPHEz